This directory contains the user-facing HTML manuals for the Regalia app
(Chinese and English versions). Each manual is a self-contained HTML file
with embedded CSS and JavaScript (no external resources).

License classification by file:
  - Regalia-v1.2.0-manual-zh.html: AGPL v3 (original Regalia work)
      Chinese user manual for Regalia v1.2.0 (current).
      Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - Regalia-v1.2.0-manual-en.html: AGPL v3 (original Regalia work)
      English user manual for Regalia v1.2.0 (current).
      Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.

The manuals are AGPL v3 because they are original documentation created by
the Regalia project, not derived from any third-party GPL work. The embedded
diagrams, wireframes, and changelog text are all original.

v1.2.0 Phase 82+++++ rev 8 (2026.7.12, same-version deep refactor):
  - Regalia-v1.2.0-manual-{zh,en}.html: Added Phase 82+++++ rev 8 changelog
    entry covering: MessageBus reflection fix (R8 renamed private field,
    replaced with public setter), proguard-rules.pro created, onDestroy
    cleanup, isPathInSandbox security hardening, _messageBus final.
    All v1.2.0 planned tasks (73-80) verified complete.
  - No new manual files; no new third-party content introduced.

