v1.2.0 Phase 78 (2026.7.11):
  - Regalia-v1.2.0-manual-{zh,en}.html (renamed from v1.1.2):
      Version references updated to v1.2.0. Added v1.2.0 changelog section
      covering: God Module split (6 Java classes + 4 JS modules), MessageBus,
      state-store.js, SonarCloud bug fixes, review board coordinate labels.
  - Old version manuals (v1.0.4–v1.1.2) have been deleted; only the current
    v1.2.0 manual is distributed. The v1.2.0 manual's Appendix A contains
    the complete historical changelog for reference.
  - No new third-party content introduced.
